name: YOUTH BRIGADE WELFARE SOCIETY
briefDescription: YOUTH BRIGADE WELFARE SOCIETY REASI We are Registered NGO in Jammu and Kashmir India Registered under SOCIETIES REGISTERED ACT OF VI OF 1998 (1941A.D) and with Planning Commission of India NGO/VOJK/2013/0056696 YBWS is committed to serve humanity YBWS. is a Non-Profit, Non Religious, Non Governmental and Non Political organization. This organization was establish in March, 2012 YBWS has been set up by a group of young professionals ,who really wants to serve and utilize their ability and skills in noble cause. The working hard in generating funds and distributing at correct places. Since it is our initial phase our main funding source is through individual supporters.
